<html>
  <head>
    <title>Div tag with transition, animation</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    div{
      border: 2px solid black;
      width:350px;
      padding:20px;
      margin-left:500px;
      margin-top: 200px;
      transition: width 2s, background 2s; 
      transition-timing-function: ease-in-out;
      animation:mymove 2s infinite;
    }
    div:hover{
      width:450px;
    }
    @keyframes mymove{
      100%{transform: rotate(360deg);}
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <div>Hey, Welcome in webpage
      <ul>In this webpage following designs: -
        <br>
        <br>
        <li>Transition with 2s for change width <!-- use ease-in-out--></li> 
        <li>div tag use change width on hovering</li>
        <li>Animation on div with rotate tab</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </body>
